                <a href="/saved-list" class="logout-btn">ğŸ“‹ ì €ì¥ëœ ë¦¬ìŠ¤íŠ¸</a>
                <a href="/inspection-management" class="logout-btn">ğŸ“‹ ê²€ì‚¬ì‹ ì²­ ê´€ë¦¬</a>
                <a href="/logout" class="logout-btn">ë¡œê·¸ì•„ì›ƒ</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="card">
            <div class="card-header">
                ğŸ” Assembly No ê²€ìƒ‰
            </div>
            <div class="card-body">
                <div style="background: #f8f9fa; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; margin-bottom: 20px;">
                    <form id="searchForm">
                        <label style="display: block; margin-bottom: 5px; font-weight: 500;">Assembly No (ë 3ìë¦¬)</label>
                        <div style="display: flex; gap: 10px; align-items: center;">
